title: USB Equipped Electrical Outlets, 4-story design w/ elevator access
posting_body: ['Get in tune with modern life.', "The Mezz at Fiddler's Green is a new kind of community.", 'A place where modern features indoors are in perfect harmony with rugged nature scenery outdoors.', 'A place where your daily schedule is a melody of endless neighborhood conveniences.', 'A place where you can dial up or down the tempo between relaxation, invigoration, or vibation.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 21', 'OR Text', '21', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text us.', 'Want more info?', 'See the link below:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 822 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Key-Less Smart Locks', '- In-home washer & dryer', '- USB Equipped Electrical Outlets', '- Luxury 1, 2, & 3 bedroom designs', '- Mountain or courtyard views', '- Ceiling fans in living room and bedrooms', '- Pendant Kitchen Lighting', 'Community Amenities', '- Cabanas, outdoor kitchen and fire features', '- Garage & open surface parking', '- Rentable storage rooms', '- Online Payments Available', '- Bike repair station & bike racks', '- Smoke-Free Community', '- 4-story design w/ elevator access', '- Indoor/outdoor flex entertainment patio', 'Pet Policy', '$300 non-refundable pet fee for the first pet.', '$200 non-refundable pet fee for the second pet.', '$20 per month per pet.', 'Cats and dogs are accepted with no weight restriction.', 'No rodents, snakes, fish tanks or birds allowed.', 'A two pet maximum is permitted.', 'Breed restrictions apply.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday: 10:00AM-6:00PM', "The Mezz at Fiddler's Green", '6440 Syracuse Way, Centennial, CO, 80111', '6s7xgYX8O17B']
